@startmindmap
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
title Kataria Stone World — functionality and system effects (current model)

* **Root: Backend + Inventory SPA**

left side

** (1) Auth /api/auth
*** Register, Login, /me
**** users + JWT; **location** + **role** scope

** (2) Customers /api/customers
*** CRUD, phone lookup
**** **customers**; bills & advances FK

** (3) Inventory /api/inventory
*** Product CRUD, stock, history
**** **products**; supplier/dealer; **product_change_history**, **inventory_history**

** (4) Bills /api/bills
*** Create GST / Non-GST
**** **bills_*** + **bill_items_***; stock down + **inventory_history** (SALE)
**** FIFO advance: **customer_advance_usage**, advance **remaining_amount**
**** Initial / line **bill_payments** → **syncBillPayment** → **financial_ledger** (CREDIT)
**** **paid_amount**, **payment_status** on bill (UI / AR, not report money total)
**** email bill (async)
*** Payment add / update / delete
**** **bill_payments**; **syncBillPayment** (active / soft-delete ledger)
*** List, sales, PDF
**** reads + PDF stream

** (5) Customer advance /api/customer/advance
*** POST advance (deposit)
**** **customer_advance**; **financial_ledger** source **ADVANCE** (CREDIT)
*** Use on bill
**** **customer_advance_usage** only — **no** extra ledger line (already credited at deposit)
*** summary, history
**** reads

** (6) Client transactions /api/client-transactions
*** PAYMENT_IN
**** **client_transactions**; ledger **CLIENT_PAYMENT_IN** (CREDIT)
*** PAYMENT_OUT, PURCHASE
**** **client_transactions**; ledger **CLIENT_TRANSACTION** (DEBIT) — **no** mirror **expenses** row
*** list
**** reads

** (7) Client purchases /api/client-purchases
*** CRUD + payments
**** **client_purchases**, **client_purchase_payments**

** (8) Expenses /api/expenses
*** CRUD
**** **expenses** table (register / lines)
**** **upsertExpenseLedger** / soft-delete → **financial_ledger** EXPENSE (DEBIT)
**** **no** **daily_budget.remaining_budget** adjustments

** (9) Employees /api/employees
*** CRUD
**** **employees**

** (10) Payroll /api/payroll
*** employee advance, salary settlement
**** **employee_payroll_ledger** + **financial_ledger** (SALARY, EMPLOYEE_ADVANCE DEBIT)
**** **no** payroll → **expenses** mirror; **no** budget in-hand hacks

** (11) Reports /api/reports
*** **GET /summary** — totalCredit, totalDebit, netBalance, expenseDebitTotal (dashboard)
*** daily-closing, payment-mode-summary, reconciliation
**** aggregates from **financial_ledger** for money totals; bills table for **invoice detail**

** (12) Daily budget /api/budget/daily
*** CRUD + status
**** **daily_budget.amount** = optional daily **cap** (informational)
**** **status** = ledger **ΣCREDIT − ΣDEBIT** for date (not stored remaining column in entity)

** (13) Suppliers / Dealers
*** **suppliers**, **dealers**

** (14) Categories /api/categories
*** **categories**

** (15) Website + Heroes
*** **website_product**, **hero_slides**

right side

** Cross-cutting
*** JWT **location** on data
*** **is_deleted** soft filters (bills, payments, expenses, ledger)
*** **financial_ledger** unique (**source_type**, **source_id**)

** Core money engine
*** **FinancialLedgerService** — **createEntry**, **syncBillPayment**, helpers
*** Idempotent active row per source key; **reactivate** if soft-deleted

** Not exposed as CRUD
*** Ledger rows only via domain services above

** External I/O
*** **EmailService** (bills)
*** **PdfService** (bills)

** Inventory SPA
*** **fetchReportsLedgerSummary** for dashboard money strip
*** same APIs as above

@endmindmap
